data.description: Welcome to this charming bi-level, nestled in the hills of Rockrimmon!  Enter into a grand foyer with vaulted ceiling and huge picture window, allowing for loads on natural light.  Upstairs you'll find beautiful laminate flooring throughout the living room, dining room and kitchen, with newer carpeting in each of the spacious bedrooms.  The living room flows into the dining room and kitchen, with stainless appliances and table-sized counter bar and a walk-out to large, wood deck.  The kitchen boasts another walk-out to the 2nd deck, offering beautiful views of the Front Range and Pikes Peak, and overlooks a beautifully landscaped and fenced backyard.  Master bedroom has adjoining 3/4 bath and dressing area.  Bedroom #2 also has a dressing area, with a 5-pc, full bath down the hall.  Back downstairs though the foyer, you'll find a floor-to-ceiling, brick fireplace, family room and two additional bedrooms and full bath.   Lovely, established neighborhood with tree-lined streets and walking distance to larger hiking trails and open space.  Easy access to I-25, shopping, dining and entertainment.  Walking distance to schools!
